{"tid":1219837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文化專題）日本傳統文化村八分","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T06:22:43.000Z","uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c10ad621099ddf3ec6c022907dee9bbd7baf16ec","tid":1219837,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:53.000Z","msg":"村八分的內容是將人們共同生活的十件重要事情中，除了協助埋葬（屍體放置的話會有屍臭甚至引發傳染病），以及滅火（置之不理的話會延燒）這兩件事情如果置之不理會將造成他人困擾外，剩下的八件事情（成人禮、結婚、生產、照顧病人、房屋改建、水災時的照顧、每年的祭拜法事、旅行）完全不進行交流及協助。<br />\n<br />\n大家知道應該點樣對待警犬及其家屬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時沈默嘅爆力比真正嘅武力更可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd857c18d42999a6d68300714ae5bc308c131be0","tid":1219837,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee0f00071ef45bdf799b9608f78d274d9117c3a","tid":1219837,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b2adca65e7f0793076500f701d165337331c02","tid":1219837,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9187becae25a39d8ad319d209e4d4ef7326a88b","tid":1219837,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b2adca65e7f0793076500f701d165337331c02","tid":1219837,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"謝推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066a24ed808e0606ed0c24350275a4403e156748","tid":1219837,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r